                            <comment id="12987970" author="ulrikem" created="Fri, 28 Jan 2011 07:27:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the fix.&lt;br/&gt;
Only a detail but wouldn&apos;t it have been cleaner to override onConfigure() in EnclosureContainer and call child.configure() from there (instead of from isVisible()), since one call to child.configure() is certainly enough.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12987971" author="ivaynberg" created="Fri, 28 Jan 2011 07:34:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;wicket keeps track if configure() has been called, and wont invoke it more then once per request.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
